Package omp2gpu.hir

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CudaAnnotation
    CudaAnnotation is used for internally representing Cuda pragmas, which contain Cuda-related user directives.
    CUDASpecifier
    CUDASpecifier represents type specifiers and modifiers for CUDA.
    CudaStdLibrary
    Repository for CUDA-supported standard library functions.
    Dim3Specifier
    Dim3Specifier represents an dim3 type specifier in CUDA, for example the round-bracketed parts of dim3 dimBlock(256,1,1);
    KernelFunctionCall
    KernelFunctionCall represents a function or method call.
    TextureSpecifier
    TextureSpecifier represents an Texture specifier in CUDA, for example texture texRef;
